metadata.name: Interstellar Needs
metadata.description:
Mankind discovered Warp Jump... and searching for new energy sources in space has become a daily task for humans.

Things have changed forever, but human needs have always remained the same.

This is a moment of basic human need... It is still a good sign that the urinary system is not damaged.

But there seems to be a threat from below. A threat or a friendly welcome? Who knows?

If he had observed cats on earth, he would have known that he had to secure himself first when peeing in an unfamiliar place.
